{"tid":277401,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求狠評] 同老人家去四日大阪 行程求插","createTime":"2017-06-09T14:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T09:07:18.000Z","uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06fcce2cacb8c4d4e19d515e13046639a99fa677","tid":277401,"uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:24:16.000Z","msg":"小妹會同屋企人 嚟緊個個星期去4日大阪<br />\n當中有一位老人家 想plan得好d 希望大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  狠評一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Day 1 - 大阪 </span><br />\n因為係晏機所以只可以行到附近嘅<strong>心齋橋</strong>同<strong>道頓崛</strong>，同埋食<strong>魚心壽司</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Day 2 - 京都 </span><br />\n嵐山竹林<br />\n-嵯峨野火車<br />\n-野宮神社<br />\n-天龍寺<br />\n-金閣寺／清水寺（因為有老人家同時間有限 去金閣寺定清水寺好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  或者有其他京都地點推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Day 3 - 奈良＋大阪 </span><br />\n- 奈良公園看鹿<br />\n- 二月堂、三月堂, 春日大社, 三条通, 五重搭,小西さくら通り商店街 <em>呢堆好唔好去？</em><br />\n- 黑門市場<br />\n<br />\n下晝翻大阪<br />\n難波<br />\n- 難波八坂神社<br />\n- 難波無印良品<br />\n- 千日前道具屋筋商店街<br />\n- Namba Nannan 大阪第一條地下街<br />\n<br />\n梅田<br />\n- <em>唔知有咩值得行 有冇ching介紹下</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Day 4 - <em>諗唔到啦</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 呢四日都係住同一間酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫下我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔係伸手黨 真係想同老人家去次開心旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2a41b8461d329bde23c1072f36ab45175d32bf","tid":277401,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:30:55.000Z","msg":"黑門市場唔使去啦 去到應該同返香港無分別"},{"pid":"a41e78a9e40c159bdaec048adf0cbdc20c2cff1a","tid":277401,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:33:18.000Z","msg":"day 2一定要好早起身，如果唔係邊去得切咁多樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金閣寺好似近嵐山少少(唔太記得)<br />\n去清水寺既話都要預返兩三個鐘行喎，除非你唔入去行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aba07414cbdf22cc4218d5052d3fd99b797b204","tid":277401,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:36:10.000Z","msg":"點解無印良品都會係行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰間好特別架?<br />\n返大阪既話，你睇下大阪周遊卡啲景點啱唔啱去，啱既就揀啲用張卡就有得免費入既"},{"pid":"cdb38310d9f64da6e093f425b7e8c818881913b1","tid":277401,"uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黑門市場唔使去啦 去到應該同返香港無分別</blockquote><br />\n台灣啲旅遊網吹到黑門市場係重點咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50d12dc70d876c6a14bb904a9be61d743b867d8","tid":277401,"uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>day 2一定要好早起身，如果唔係邊去得切咁多樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金閣寺好似近嵐山少少(唔太記得)<br />\n去清水寺既話都要預返兩三個鐘行喎，除非你唔入去行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個日下晝真係係諗唔掂 想同老人家睇多啲有日本風味啲嘅景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2653e9383ad82a08909472933d90c662df5150d","tid":277401,"uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解無印良品都會係行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰間好特別架?<br />\n返大阪既話，你睇下大阪周遊卡啲景點啱唔啱去，啱既就揀啲用張卡就有得免費入既</blockquote><br />\n但好似好多地點都好偏遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d4888484fcd3a929cc40a04a5ee961a386cef6","tid":277401,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:30:29.000Z","msg":"清水寺裝修緊喎<br />\n去伏見稻荷啦<br />\n<br />\n上次同老人家去5日，得1日響大阪，日日響京都上吓山睇下寺咁佢地好夠開心"},{"pid":"8bfcc27b98e4de6f0b40e95c6a5923eab275f32a","tid":277401,"uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>清水寺裝修緊喎<br />\n去伏見稻荷啦<br />\n<br />\n上次同老人家去5日，得1日響大阪，日日響京都上吓山睇下寺咁佢地好夠開心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食野呢 有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc0fb37f22b76d7a0417a9a9d0d0c17c276b364","tid":277401,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"share吓我個行程你睇下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n帶住2個6字頭去<br />\n<br />\nday1 <br />\n搭飛機，坐巴士去京都<br />\n去到酒店搞掂已要食dinner，行激安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nday2<br />\n一早出發去鞍馬貴船食流水麵，響貴船hea耐咗，3點去到比叡口上唔切寺但照搭咗吊車上山頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後落去行四条果堆旺嘢<br />\n<br />\nday3 <br />\n伏見稻荷，行咗上少少個山<br />\n行伏見地區，睇酒廠睇寺田屋，hea耐咗無搭到船觀光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出返京都站行aeon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nday4<br />\n出大阪行心齋橋，老人家覺得悶同易攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nday5<br />\n極hea行京都站附近之後走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同老人家去一定要預鬆d預慢d同唔好plan死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749de2ecaba76a88b228f7eeac8350497f50bcdd","tid":277401,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>清水寺裝修緊喎<br />\n去伏見稻荷啦<br />\n<br />\n上次同老人家去5日，得1日響大阪，日日響京都上吓山睇下寺咁佢地好夠開心</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食野呢 有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見有咩老人家啱食就食咩咋，有個有糖尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未食過既話去溫野菜食次黑毛和牛啦，4500yen抵到傻，雖然係全國嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n京都我就食過豆腐懷石，都唔係太貴<br />\n<br />\n其他係9食，京都無咩伏中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9f586abe19638d3e181bb549a4346d7e8790a0","tid":277401,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"行撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca4a9cfb0e0d071db73df770998173bbbb23d61","tid":277401,"uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推輪椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe1d28717a72a51752baf75dc3976d7d581742b","tid":277401,"uid":35698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>行撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推輪椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔好去清水寺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8cd62bfadcd8c4af27bf73cc90eccb6e7bccac","tid":277401,"uid":50666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04