g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔好去清水寺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n更加去唔到伏見</blockquote><br />\n唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伏見唔上山都有嘢睇，老人家都去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bfffdbd7b534769764f678b1dc02ee558f1776","tid":277401,"uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>行撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推輪椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔好去清水寺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n更加去唔到伏見</blockquote><br />\n唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伏見唔上山都有嘢睇，老人家都去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n附近都有野睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e580a15c78fe772e5028a133e90632880f19e10e","tid":277401,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小妹會同屋企人 嚟緊個個星期去4日大阪<br />\n當中有一位老人家 想plan得好d 希望大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  狠評一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Day 1 - 大阪 </span><br />\n因為係晏機所以只可以行到附近嘅<strong>心齋橋</strong>同<strong>道頓崛</strong>，同埋食<strong>魚心壽司</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Day 2 - 京都 </span><br />\n嵐山竹林<br />\n-嵯峨野火車<br />\n-野宮神社<br />\n-天龍寺<br />\n-金閣寺／清水寺（因為有老人家同時間有限 去金閣寺定清水寺好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  或者有其他京都地點推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Day 3 - 奈良＋大阪 </span><br />\n- 奈良公園看鹿<br />\n- 二月堂、三月堂, 春日大社, 三条通, 五重搭,小西さくら通り商店街 <em>呢堆好唔好去？</em><br />\n- 黑門市場<br />\n<br />\n下晝翻大阪<br />\n難波<br />\n- 難波八坂神社<br />\n- 難波無印良品<br />\n- 千日前道具屋筋商店街<br />\n- Namba Nannan 大阪第一條地下街<br />\n<br />\n梅田<br />\n- <em>唔知有咩值得行 有冇ching介紹下</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Day 4 - <em>諗唔到啦</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw 呢四日都係住同一間酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家幫下我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔係伸手黨 真係想同老人家去次開心旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nD2: 建議去清水寺 雖然有部分地方做緊維修 但其他地方都OK<br />\n       尤其是X年坂 真係值得一行<br />\n       順手可以坐巴士去埋京都八阪神社再落去祗園<br />\n<br />\nD3:去奈良撚鹿OK 但係要行入去春日大社 老人家行唔行到先<br />\n      其實可以順便去埋宇治HEA下<br />\n<br />\n個人認為 京都比較適合老人家去<br />\n因為無咁chur 好多景點都有車直達"},{"pid":"79f348bcce28b3bcdbc787fb29c92a2de8620df2","tid":277401,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"有老人家緊係跟鴨仔團<br />\n<br />\n仲自己PLAN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e66e56bde611a710071a793efc58ec00119c934","tid":277401,"uid":38071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"老人家信唔信佛架？<br />\n信嘅話上高野山行下啦<br />\n不過我就算唔信都好有興趣行:p <br />\n而且雖然話山，但路其實好平所以好易行 <br />\n不過最好weekday去行啦，無咁多人"}]}